      {
        "title": "APS-C Sensor",
        "description": "Equipped with a 24.1-megapixel APS-C CMOS sensor and DIGIC 8 image processor, the EOS R100 can deliver outstanding image quality even in low-light. It has an ISO range of 100 to 12,800."
      },
      {
        "title": "Scene Intelligent Auto",
        "description": "Just put the EOS R100 into Scene Intelligent Auto mode and let it handle everything else. The camera intelligently detects the scene automatically and applies the best settings to capture the best image."
      },
      {
        "title": "Ergonomic Design",
        "description": "Based on decades of experience making quality cameras for photographers, the way the buttons are positioned on EOS R100 are carefully considered. The textured grip exudes an elegant and practical feel for photographers holding the camera."
      },
      {
        "title": "Connectivity",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "Wi-Fi",
        "description": "Transfer files wirelessly and quickly from the EOS R100 to your smart device or PC using high-speed 2.4 GHz built-in Wi-Fi*. The EOS R100 supports Wi-Fi Protected Access 2 (WPA2) for added file security on wireless networks."
